3.Fish_Trends ReadMe

Loads watershed, park boundary, and stream shapefiles.

Imports three-pass electrofishing summary data.

Filters species and streams with sufficient sampling (≥5 years).

Matches sampling locations to named hydrography lines.

Fits per-stream linear models of adult density over time.

Maps slope results across the park, highlighting significant trends.

Generates time-series plots of adult density by stream for each species.

Exports all trend maps and plots as PDFs for review.